 \exp (\theta_i \mathbf G_i) = \mathtt I + \mathtt G_i\sin(\theta_i) + \mathtt G_i^2(1-\cos(\theta_i)) 
\exp(\theta_x\cdot \mathtt G_x) = \mathtt I +\begin{bmatrix}0 & 0& 0\\0 & 0& -1\\0 & 1& 0\end{bmatrix}\sin(\theta_x) + \begin{bmatrix}0 & 0& 0\\0 & -1& 0\\0 & 0& -1\end{bmatrix}(1-\cos(\theta_x)) 
\quad\quad\quad\quad\quad\quad\quad\quad\quad\quad\quad\quad\quad\quad\quad=\begin{bmatrix}1 & 0& 0\\0 & \cos(\theta_x)& -\sin(\theta_x)\\0 & \sin(\theta_x)& \cos(\theta_x)\end{bmatrix}
